    - Added imports: QueryBuildRequest, QueryConstraint, QueryElements, analyze_query_intent, HasUsage
    - Updated constructor to accept optimizer and template_manager
    - Fixed query parsing to use analyze_query_intent()
    - Added runtime checks and delegation for optimizer/template methods
  2. /core/services/query_builder.py
    - Updated QueryValidator initialization to inject dependencies
    - Fixed return types: Result[str] → Result[QueryOptimizationResult]
    - Fixed method parameters to match actual sub-service signatures

